{"title":"0003. 无重复字符的最长字串","date":"2020-10-23T11:35:17.467Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 23, 2020","L":"10/23/2020","MM-DD":"10-23"},"updated":"2020-10-10T07:48:53.000Z","content":"<p><a href=\"leetcode/0003-en\">English</a>｜ 简体中文</p>\n<h2 id=\"题目描述\">题目描述<a title=\"#题目描述\" href=\"#题目描述\"></a></h2>\n<p>给定一个字符串，请你找出其中不含有重复字符的 <strong>最长子串</strong> 的长度。</p>\n<p><strong>示例 1：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong>“abcabcbb”<br>\n**输出：**3<br>\n**解释：**因为无重复字符的最长子串是 “abc”，所以其长度为 3。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例 2：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong>“bbbbb”<br>\n**输出：**1<br>\n**解释：**因为无重复字符的最长子串是 “b”，所以其长度为 1。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例 3：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong>“pwwkew”<br>\n**输出：**3<br>\n**解释：**因为无重复字符的最长子串是 “wke”，所以其长度为 3。<br>\n请注意，你的答案必须是 <strong>子串</strong> 的长度，“pwke” 是一个 <em>子序列</em>，不是子串。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"题解\">题解<a title=\"#题解\" href=\"#题解\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight swift\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">lengthOfLongestSubstring</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"number\">_</span> s: String)</span></span> -&gt; <span class=\"type\">Int</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> chars = [<span class=\"type\">Character</span>: <span class=\"type\">Int</span>]()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> length : <span class=\"type\">Int</span> = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> i : <span class=\"type\">Int</span> = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (j, ch) <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> s.enumerated() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> head = chars[ch] &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                i = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(head + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, i)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            chars[ch] = j</span><br><span class=\"line\">            length = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(j - i + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, length)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> length</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","link":"leetcode/0003","comments":true,"plink":"https://oreodu.github.io/leetcode/0003/","toc":[{"id":"题目描述","title":"题目描述","index":"1"},{"id":"题解","title":"题解","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Oreo Du","link":"<a href=\"https://oreodu.github.io/leetcode/0003/\" title=\"0003. 无重复字符的最长字串\">https://oreodu.github.io/leetcode/0003/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}